            <h2 class="archive__item-title">First-class array support</h2>
          

          
            <div class="archive__item-excerpt">
              <p>Multidimensional arrays are the primary data structure of Nial, and much of its standard library is based around their usage and manipulation.</p>

            </div>
          

          
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  
    <div class="feature__item">
      <div class="archive__item">
        

